nodes.text: Cinnabar was a fathier female that mated with Crimson Pavane, and gave birth to the fathier named Vermilion in 31 ABY as a result.

By around 34 ABY, Vermilion had become a racing fathier on the planet Cantonica. Cinnabar was listed as the fathier's dam on race programs, including one collected by the Resistance mechanic Rose Tico and added to her diary.
Cinnabar was first mentioned in the 2018 replica journal The Last Jedi: Rose Tico: Resistance Fighter, which was written by Jason Fry.
